      (added to PATH in ~/.bashrc.d/nvim.sh)
config: https://github.com/beatmax/nvim-config
install nerd fonts: https://gist.github.com/matthewjberger/7dd7e079f282f8138a9dc3b045ebefa0
configure terminal to use 'JetbrainsMono Nerd Font'
